<body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" tts:textAlign="center">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18.598" end="00:00:22.177">En, to, En, to, tre, fire.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.255" end="00:00:23.496"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23.558" end="00:00:25.665">Hvis du holder af James Brown musik,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.665" end="00:00:27.557">f&#229;r du en virkelig dejlig aften.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.557" end="00:00:29.731">I aften fejrer vi Black Velvet</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.731" end="00:00:33.816">James Brown, Jr.'s 62 &#229;rs f&#248;dselsdag.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33.816" end="00:00:35.870" region="top"> Whoo, 62!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:36.439" end="00:00:38.487" region="top"> S&#229; nu vil jeg bede jeg give et stort bifald,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:38.487" end="00:00:39.718" region="top"> for vi har en ung mand</p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.718" end="00:00:41.503" region="top"> der kommer p&#229; scenen nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:41.503" end="00:00:43.646">Han har v&#230;ret med i David Letterman Show.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.646" end="00:00:45.731">Giv et bifald, m&#248;d og byd velkommen til</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.731" end="00:00:49.913">Black Velvet James Brown, Jr.!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.913" end="00:00:52.226"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52.226" end="00:00:53.898"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53.898" end="00:00:59.189">&#9834; Det en en mands verden. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.189" end="00:01:05.490">&#9834; Men jeg ville v&#230;re ingenting, ingenting ... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05.490" end="00:01:06.648">- Jeg har spillet James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.648" end="00:01:13.882">siden jeg var 14 &#229;r gammel.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.882" end="00:01:16.398"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16.398" end="00:01:17.857"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17.857" end="00:01:21.189"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21.189" end="00:01:25.774"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25.774" end="00:01:29.677">Men nu vil jeg til at lave Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.677" end="00:01:52.332"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52.486" end="00:01:54.356" region="top"> Mit f&#248;rste album med originale numre</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.356" end="00:01:58.013" region="top"> udkommer 25. januar.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.013" end="00:02:01.149">Jeg har k&#230;mpet i mere end 42 &#229;r</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.149" end="00:02:02.890">for at klare mig i denne industri</p>
      <p begin="00:02:02.890" end="00:02:04.606">og i en alder af 62 &#229;r,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.606" end="00:02:06.648">er jeg ved at finde den rette vej.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.956" end="00:02:10.939">Jeg har aldrig tjent nok</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.939" end="00:02:13.794">p&#229; musikken til at kunne leve af det.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.794" end="00:02:15.857">Men jeg h&#229;ber at dette album</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.857" end="00:02:17.304">vil blive et vendepunkt for mig,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.304" end="00:02:20.111">at jeg kan leve af musik nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.168" end="00:02:26.690">Hey, mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.690" end="00:02:28.659">Jeg finder lidt vand til dig, OK?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.659" end="00:02:30.004">Hey, mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.004" end="00:02:30.683">Det er min fugl.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.683" end="00:02:32.494">G&#248;r mig vred.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32.494" end="00:02:33.628">Jeg bliver vred, jeg g&#229;r v&#230;k fra det,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.628" end="00:02:35.364">g&#229;r ind i det rum, lukker d&#248;ren,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.364" end="00:02:37.170">og lader ham r&#229;be det han vil.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:37.861" end="00:02:38.897">Og jag har mit eget lille sted,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.897" end="00:02:40.429">det er ikke det jeg &#248;nsker,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.429" end="00:02:43.035">men Gud ske tak, har jeg tak over hovedet.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.056" end="00:02:45.363">N&#229;r jeg g&#229;r ind i min lille lejlighed</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.363" end="00:02:46.945">og l&#229;ser min d&#248;r,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:46.945" end="00:02:48.565">s&#229; har jeg fred.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48.565" end="00:02:50.325">N&#229;r n&#229;r jeg g&#229;r ned til ghettoen,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.325" end="00:02:53.051">g&#229;r ind i elevatoren,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.051" end="00:02:54.632">n&#229;r man kommer ind i den,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54.232" end="00:02:55.369">det er der problemerne begynder.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.369" end="00:02:56.898">Du ved aldrig</p>
      <p begin="00:02:56.898" end="00:02:58.994">hvad der sker i disse ting.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:58.994" end="00:03:00.482">Fyren nedenfor,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.482" end="00:03:02.183">hans navn er Alfred,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.183" end="00:03:03.022">en rigtig god fyr, gjorde ingen fortr&#230;d.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.022" end="00:03:04.598">En kirkens mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.598" end="00:03:06.544">De sk&#248;d l&#248;s p&#229; hans sted.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.544" end="00:03:07.565">Han viste mig alle hullerne</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07.565" end="00:03:08.289">hvor de sk&#248;d op i stedet.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.289" end="00:03:09.071">Jeg sagde, wow, mand.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.071" end="00:03:10.550">Jeg sagde,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.550" end="00:03:12.823">"&#216;h, jeg kunne ikke leve p&#229; f&#248;rste sal."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.823" end="00:03:14.391">N&#229;r det bliver for</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.391" end="00:03:16.092">vildt i ghettoen,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.092" end="00:03:17.808">tager jeg til min mors hus</p>
      <p begin="00:03:17.808" end="00:03:19.537">og jeg sover i hendes k&#230;lder.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.862" end="00:03:33.477">S&#229; jeg kommer her</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33.477" end="00:03:35.794">og det er hvor jeg overnatter.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:35.794" end="00:03:37.051">Indtil n&#230;ste dag,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37.051" end="00:03:38.838">jeg tager mig af deres &#230;rinder,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:38.838" end="00:03:39.884">s&#248;rger for det hele</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.884" end="00:03:43.414">for at vi kan have tag over hovederne.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.707" end="00:03:47.142">Jeg tager gerne lidt af dette</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.142" end="00:03:48.735">i en lille kugle.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50.722" end="00:03:53.068">Kom ogs&#229; disse i.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.486" end="00:03:56.661">Hey, hvordan er risen?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:56.829" end="00:03:58.127">- Lad mig se?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:59.894" end="00:04:01.813">Bare lidt mere.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:01.951" end="00:04:04.880">- Jeg kom fra en familie p&#229; otte.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:04.942" end="00:04:07.772">Hovedsagen er at passe p&#229;</p>
      <p begin="00:04:07.772" end="00:04:11.547">min mor og g&#248;re hvad jeg kan.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.454" end="00:04:14.409" region="top"> - Det er min lille dreng,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.409" end="00:04:16.520" region="top"> og jeg elsker ham.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.626" end="00:04:18.297" region="top"> Han vasker mit t&#248;j.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.467" end="00:04:19.206" region="top"> Han g&#248;r huset rent.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.206" end="00:04:20.684" region="top"> P&#229; Valentins dag,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.684" end="00:04:23.291" region="top"> gav han mig en &#230;ske slik.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:23.291" end="00:04:24.646" region="top"> Min lille baby er</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.646" end="00:04:25.871" region="top"> lige s&#229; s&#248;d som det slik.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:25.871" end="00:04:27.567">- Jeg pr&#248;ver bare at give</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.567" end="00:04:28.273">hende et fredfyldt liv,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.273" end="00:04:29.398">og</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29.398" end="00:04:31.440">s&#229; hun ikke skal bekymre sig om</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.440" end="00:04:33.038">regninger og den slags.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.038" end="00:04:34.203">Jeg tog det p&#229; mine skuldre</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.203" end="00:04:35.913">og jeg virkelig,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:35.913" end="00:04:37.553">jeg vidste nok ikke hvad det var jeg kastede mig ud i.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.553" end="00:04:38.214">Men nu er jeg i det.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.214" end="00:04:39.802">Det vil jeg ikke &#230;ndre.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:39.802" end="00:04:40.970">S&#229; det eneste jeg kan pr&#248;ve at</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.970" end="00:04:42.685">g&#248;re er at f&#229; noget til at lykkes,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.685" end="00:04:44.012">hvor jeg kan tjene en rimelig indkomst,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.012" end="00:04:46.923">s&#229; jeg kan leve og lade leve.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.923" end="00:04:49.739">Og det er det eneste jeg &#248;nsker i livet nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:49.847" end="00:04:56.578"/>
      <p begin="00:04:56.578" end="00:05:00.314">&#9834; Vi k&#248;rer rundt og rundt igen.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.314" end="00:05:04.916">&#9834;Hvor det stopper, ved ingen. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:04.916" end="00:05:08.256">&#9834; Det er en kold, kold verden &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.656" end="00:05:12.156">&#9834; Det er en kold, kold verden. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.939" end="00:05:15.856">&#9834; Hvordan kan vi stopper forandringerne, &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:15.856" end="00:05:20.897">&#9834; der sker i Amerika i dag? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.701" end="00:05:34.686">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.124" end="00:05:43.231">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.231" end="00:05:46.939">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage til den Gyldne Regel. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:46.939" end="00:05:48.645">&#9834; Oh. Ah. Uh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.105" end="00:05:50.612">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.612" end="00:05:55.148">&#9834; G&#229; tilbage til den Gyldne Regel. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.148" end="00:05:57.856">&#9834; D&#230;mp det lidt &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.856" end="00:06:11.472"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11.472" end="00:06:13.064">- Det er en sang</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13.064" end="00:06:15.023">fra den nye plade, "No Time For Dreaming".</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15.023" end="00:06:16.148">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.148" end="00:06:17.274">og the Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.274" end="00:06:18.731">Jeg kan ikke tro</p>
      <p begin="00:06:18.731" end="00:06:20.064">at du kom ud af intet</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.064" end="00:06:22.273">som n&#230;sten ukendt for os.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.273" end="00:06:24.473">Har du indspillet f&#248;r?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.596" end="00:06:25.890">- Nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:25.890" end="00:06:28.431">Det er f&#248;rste jeg jeg udkommer.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28.431" end="00:06:29.958">- Jeg ved du har optr&#229;dt.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:29.958" end="00:06:31.039">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31.539" end="00:06:32.527">- Som Black Velvet.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32.527" end="00:06:33.649">-Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:33.649" end="00:06:34.939">- S&#229; nu optr&#230;der du som-</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.939" end="00:06:36.666">som Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:36.666" end="00:06:37.677">- Jah, jah.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.677" end="00:06:38.898">- Jamen, du har bestemt et fantastisk band</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38.898" end="00:06:39.728">bag dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.728" end="00:06:41.265">Og selvf&#248;lgelig</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.265" end="00:06:42.898">med folkene over p&#229; Daptone,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:42.898" end="00:06:44.058">du ved,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.058" end="00:06:44.881">det er et storartet hold.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.881" end="00:06:46.190">Og du har set</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.190" end="00:06:48.866">hvad der skete med Sharon Jones, som, - Ja, ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:48.866" end="00:06:50.928">du ved, like som du,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:50.928" end="00:06:52.469">gik fra komplet ukendt til</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52.484" end="00:06:55.048">hvem ved hvilke h&#248;jder du kan n&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.048" end="00:06:56.455">S&#229; det,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56.455" end="00:06:58.647">det m&#229; v&#230;re et sp&#230;ndende &#248;jeblik for dig?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:58.647" end="00:07:01.398">- Jeg tror Gud lige har svarret p&#229; mine b&#248;nner,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.398" end="00:07:03.440">du ved, det bare ligesom.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.440" end="00:07:05.606">Jeg spurgte mig selv, hvorfor det tog s&#229; lang tid,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:05.606" end="00:07:07.023">men du kan ikke stille sp&#248;rgsm&#229;lstegn ved Gud</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07.023" end="00:07:08.981">n&#229;r han vil g&#248;re ting.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:08.981" end="00:07:11.915">S&#229; i min h&#248;je alder begyndte det bare at komme.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:11.915" end="00:07:13.482">- Hvad er det n&#230;ste?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.482" end="00:07:14.939">Jeg mener, t&#230;nker du stort?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:14.939" end="00:07:16.706">- Jeg mener at der er ingen gr&#230;nser.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:16.706" end="00:07:18.981">- Tillykke med denne fantastiske plade.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:18.981" end="00:07:20.296">Uanset hvad der sker med den,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20.296" end="00:07:22.189">er det et fint stykke kunst.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22.189" end="00:07:24.498">Charles Bradley p&#229; WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:24.667" end="00:07:27.897"/>
      <p begin="00:07:27.897" end="00:07:33.231">&#9834; Denne verden g&#229;r i flammer. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.231" end="00:07:38.647">&#9834; Og ingen vil tage skylden. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:38.647" end="00:07:43.821">&#9834; Fort&#230;l mig ikke, hvordan jeg skal leve mit liv. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:43.821" end="00:07:49.276">&#9834; N&#229;r du aldrig har f&#248;lt smerten. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.276" end="00:07:55.314">&#9834; Ohhh. Ahhh. Ohhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.314" end="00:07:57.856">&#9834;Ohhh.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:57.856" end="00:08:00.569">&#9834; Kan de ikke se jeg gr&#230;der? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:00.569" end="00:08:02.400" region="top"> &#9834; Ohhh... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:02.400" end="00:08:04.315"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04.315" end="00:08:05.564" region="top"> - Jeg ved ikke hvor mange kunstnere</p>
      <p begin="00:08:05.564" end="00:08:07.230" region="top"> der har v&#230;ret over 62 &#229;r gamle</p>
      <p begin="00:08:07.230" end="00:08:08.955" region="top"> og udgivet deres debut plade.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:09.722" end="00:08:11.458" region="top"> Han er m&#229;ske den f&#248;rste.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.284" end="00:08:14.441" region="top"> - Denne fyr har fattet det,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.441" end="00:08:16.440" region="top"> f&#229;r gang i den, efter min mening.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:16.440" end="00:08:18.715" region="top"> - Han har arbejdet meget h&#229;rdt i lang tid.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:18.838" end="00:08:20.357" region="top"> Og jeg h&#229;ber at-</p>
      <p begin="00:08:20.357" end="00:08:21.232" region="top"> nok folk kan h&#248;re ham synge,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:21.232" end="00:08:22.647">s&#229; at-</p>
      <p begin="00:08:22.647" end="00:08:23.856">han kan skabe sig det liv han &#248;nsker sig,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.856" end="00:08:25.632">og tage sig af sin familie.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:25.632" end="00:08:27.118"/>
      <p begin="00:08:27.118" end="00:08:30.190">&#9834; Uh. Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.190" end="00:08:32.606">&#9834; Jeg taler til dig t&#248;s &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:32.606" end="00:08:34.023">&#9834; Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34.023" end="00:08:36.125">&#9834; Kun du ... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36.125" end="00:08:37.814">Jeg gik til Gabe</p>
      <p begin="00:08:37.814" end="00:08:39.981">fordi jeg mente at han ved hvad han g&#248;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:39.981" end="00:08:41.606">Og jeg f&#248;lte at han kunne give mig en hj&#230;lpende h&#229;nd</p>
      <p begin="00:08:41.606" end="00:08:44.148">hvor jeg kan komme ind i musik branchen.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:44.148" end="00:08:48.040">Det eneste jeg vidste var hvordan jeg kom op p&#229; en scene og optr&#230;de.</p>
